{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Uh, it just happened, and it was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we arrived at the Straf company.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, I found out something 10 seconds after I got in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Straf company was right within the camp of Birkenau, but there was a wall around it with a door to go in, OK?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Straf company, eh, we were supposed to last two days, three days at the most.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I lasted for almost a month.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By luck-- not only by sheer luck, but, uh, I also had somebody to protect me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And funny enough at that time, in retrospect, I did not think of my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got help from somebody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got help from the two guys that arrived with me from Belgium that used to work in Kanada.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Story. ?] Anyhow, I-- down there, we had a Kommando Fuhrer, which was the man in charge of the, uh, thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we walked out every morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, the first morning, we walked out, and there was an irrigation to be done down there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw the first three killings of Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Josef Eckhart, Unterscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, he threw them in down there, and he stomped at him with his boots until they drowned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another thing that was very, very [? insignificant ?] is that, uh, dead people, any dead person, was referred to as pieces, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, when the guy says [GERMAN] meant 10 dead people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very common term, OK?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And did it matter if they were Jews or not?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That didn't make any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a dead person, that's all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Um--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
